{"tid":1586264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗站上蓋千萬住宅業主:「8．21都沒封站，我們要行，示威者都讓路，今次封站一早拉封鎖線，極度影響我」","createTime":"2019-09-22T01:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T02:24:04.000Z","uid":51271,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d21fdeeccaeaaeefd8620f751a2a1dff03ae87e0","tid":1586264,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190922/s00001/1569088437188/%e9%9d%9c%e5%9d%90%e5%89%8d4%e5%b0%8f%e6%99%82%e9%97%9c%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e7%ab%99-%e8%a1%97%e5%9d%8a%e5%8f%96%e6%b6%88%e5%87%ba%e8%a1%8c%e6%89%b9%e6%93%be%e6%b0%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190922%2Fs00001%2F1569088437188%2F%25e9%259d%259c%25e5%259d%2590%25e5%2589%258d4%25e5%25b0%258f%25e6%2599%2582%25e9%2597%259c%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e7%25ab%2599-%25e8%25a1%2597%25e5%259d%258a%25e5%258f%2596%25e6%25b6%2588%25e5%2587%25ba%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%2589%25b9%25e6%2593%25be%25e6%25b0%2591&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FQHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=fbf1fe17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190922%2Fs00001%2F1569088437188%2F%25e9%259d%259c%25e5%259d%2590%25e5%2589%258d4%25e5%25b0%258f%25e6%2599%2582%25e9%2597%259c%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e7%25ab%2599-%25e8%25a1%2597%25e5%259d%258a%25e5%258f%2596%25e6%25b6%2588%25e5%2587%25ba%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%2589%25b9%25e6%2593%25be%25e6%25b0%2591&h=b6b85bd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190922/s00001/1569088437188/%e9%9d%9c%e5%9d%90%e5%89%8d4%e5%b0%8f%e6%99%82%e9%97%9c%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e7%ab%99-%e8%a1%97%e5%9d%8a%e5%8f%96%e6%b6%88%e5%87%ba%e8%a1%8c%e6%89%b9%e6%93%be%e6%b0%91</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】港鐵昨日因應屯門遊行及元朗站靜坐而關閉西鐵線屯門站及元朗站，當中元朗站在靜坐4小時前、即昨午3時已關閉。有元朗居民批評港鐵提早4小時封站是「無謂」及擾民，有人更為此取消外出，「驚出去返不到來」。<br />\n<br />\n「光復屯門公園」遊行昨午2時起步，另元朗站靜坐則由7時開始。港鐵昨早10時宣布，因應有公眾活動評估風險，並與相關政府部門商討後，考慮到乘客及員工安全，西鐵線屯門站昨午1時起關閉，元朗站3時關閉。<br />\n<br />\n屯門站商舖下午12時許已落閘，近D出口有逾20名防暴警察駐守，其餘多個出口均設封鎖線，有港鐵職員看守。港鐵職員在下午約1時開始封站，同時有人跑入閘。<br />\n千萬買港鐵上蓋 「極影響我」<br />\n<br />\n元朗站則於下午3時關閉。街坊李太原定帶兒子上興趣班，中午得知3時元朗站關閉，感非常憤怒，致電元朗警署問「你們到底搞乜？」警員反問她為何致電警署。住在元朗站上蓋物業的徐先生昨晚原約了朋友食飯，因封站而告吹，「我驚出去返不到來」。他去年為住近港鐵站，以近千萬元買入單位，「8．21都沒封站，我們要行，示威者都讓路，今次封站一早拉封鎖線，極度影響我」。居住元朗35年的他說從未見元朗如此多警察，是7．21後才見到，稱昨晚7時才有人靜坐，一早封站是「無謂」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n黨鐵同狗狗諗住用封站一招令民意逆轉，但次次都唔得，仲比人屌到反檯。<br />\n手足們，記得be humble，以禮待人，街坊相信手足係好人呢樣係非常重要。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"983aed30a28526d86212bc3879fc022fde4061b2","tid":1586264,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a776e41fcf169bc58d36cc5ec80e489bb796e3e5","tid":1586264,"uid":85629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:06:30.000Z","msg":"對人民humble<br />\n對暴政鼠輩要企硬"},{"pid":"2da7a5f57410670f9cb65a7ffe14952d3d8b72f6","tid":1586264,"uid":247892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:07:59.000Z","msg":"警署電話可以cut左佢啦<br />\n問人做乜打電話過黎?<br />\n叫你接電話講呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b423b13d421b5fd5647eda232f3bfeec14ed94","tid":1586264,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7478918f9c6742200ce42649fdc7e51260d6f76c","tid":1586264,"uid":72065,"like":0,"disli